<span id="freeTextContainer2706868031357404141">I have never read a memoir before but after reading Lene Fogelberg&apos;s story I may just pick some more up.<br/><br/>This memoir was absolutely beautiful. Her story and the way that it was written is amazing. I didn&apos;t feel like I was reading a memoir or &quot;biography&quot; type book. It kept me engaged and I would give it 10 stars if it went that high.<br/><br/>I highly recommend this memoir.<br/><br/>Thank you Lene for sharing your story with me!!</span>
  <span id="freeText2706868031357404141" style="display:none">I have never read a memoir before but after reading Lene Fogelberg's story I may just pick some more up.<br /><br />This memoir was absolutely beautiful. Her story and the way that it was written is amazing. I didn't feel like I was reading a memoir or "biography" type book. It kept me engaged and I would give it 10 stars if it went that high.<br /><br />I highly recommend this memoir.<br /><br />Thank you Lene for sharing your story with me!!</span>
