  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1449136787?book_show_action=true">Nov 22, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marian Sofferin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marian Sofferin" href="/user/show/16708364-marian-sofferin">Marian Sofferin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1449136787" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18115224499406804580">I had to stop reading this at 75% completed since I related to it on a very personal level. I related to the author so closely with her experience of long term illness that I started feeling anxiety. When she entered the hospital for open heart surgery I had to stop. I rated this a 5 since her writing was very realistic. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


